data.description: LAKEFRONT MASTERPIECE!! COMPLETELY RENOVATED WITH NO EXPENSE SPARED!!! Over $200,000 in updates and renovations! You must see to believe this jaw-dropping lakefront masterpiece with over 2,000 square feet smack dab on Lake Tarpon with stunning views throughout! Reimagined and customized to an ideal open floorplan. Four large bedrooms, (double master suites), 3.5 baths and updated to the max. A chef's dream kitchen awaits behind the exquisite front doors of your new home. Efficiently unload the groceries to the superior quality kitchen cabinets with soft close doors & drawers. Cook with top of the line, newer stainless steel energy efficient LG appliances, handpicked Brazilian premium granite & custom faucets. Thick & durable porcelain tiles flow throughout as you walk back to the astonishing oversized great room set up for projection television, complete with built-in features, plus vaulted & custom solid wood coffered ceilings… stunning! To your right, is one of two primary suites. His & her shower heads await in the walk-in shower deluxe spa as well as his and her closets with custom racks & shelving. On the other side of this split floor plan, you get a full-sized laundry room with modern cabinets, washer, dryer and utility sink. The second primary suite is situated for ultimate privacy and its bath allows outdoor access. One of the large secondary bedrooms has a bath that has been discretely modified with a nod to disabled/elderly needs. There is also a convenient extra half bath in the living area. Fishing paradise as you walk through the newer double pane infinity sliders, giving you proper Florida living views on the daily. The home is fenced and has a wood dock with electric connectivity, an outdoor half-kitchen, and partially covered porch. Windows have aluminum bolt on shutters for hurricane protection. Entire home is equipped to provide the utmost protection in case of a storm, additional security measures include doorbell… features providing you security as well as insurance discounts; There is additional storage provided by a large, sound proofed storage room! Sellers also have a transferable home warranty! This home has it all! NOT JUST A HOME BUT A LIFESTYLE. Ideal location, fantastic dining & shopping nearby, top notched schools, beaches galore, centrally located to get you anywhere! THIS IS HOW LIFE SHOULD BE LIVED!!! LAKE SIDE PARADISE!
